      <title>日本央行维持关键利率不变，日元兑美元跌破157</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/yen-drops-to-fresh-34-year-low-as-boj-keeps-key-rate-unchanged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行表示货币政策将保持宽松，日元兑美元汇率跌至 34 年来新低，并突破 157 的水平，加剧了当局可能很快干预市场以阻止日元贬值的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/yen-drops-to-fresh-34-year-low-as-boj-keeps-key-rate-unchanged</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:34:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
